# Enforce LF line endings everywhere (Windows / macOS / Linux) so the repository
# stays byte-identical across platforms. These attributes override core.autocrlf.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary files: never apply line-ending conversion (explicit safety on top of
# Git's auto-detection, e.g. for vendored libs and README screenshots).
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.ico  binary
*.dll  binary
*.lib  binary
*.exp  binary
*.pdb  binary
*.exe  binary
